longest_rain.status: Today's rainstorm ranked 5th on our record table for the length of the storm as it lasted 22.9 hours; it delivered 7.68mm of rain at a maximum rate of 4.1mm per hour.  Rain fell for 37.2 hours on 04 January 2025 creating a new record that still lasts.  The storm produced a total of 36.8mm with a maximum intensity of 4.6mm per hour.
